            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-183627921" class="vote-count">10</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-183627921" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="183627921">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2429292/">优游卒岁</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2009-11-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这是我在大学所接触到的第一本美学书，一下引起了我对美学的兴趣，整整迷了四年。作为美学的入门书籍，这本应该说是最好的。写得很可读也很有激情。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="164238302">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
